headline: Fortive: Modest Recovery, But Growth Remains Elusive
summary: Fortiv Corporation (FTV) Q3 FY25 revenue grew 2.4% year-over-year, driven by the IOS segment, while adjusted EBITDA margin expanded to 30.1%.

headline: 2 Profitable Stocks Worth Your Attention and 1 We Avoid
summary: Even if a company is profitable, it doesn’t always mean it’s a great investment. Some struggle to maintain growth, face looming threats, or fail to reinvest wisely, limiting their future potential.
